SIMPLE: quodlibet
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quodlibet
<hw>Quod"li*bet</hw> <pr>(kw⟦ocr⟧d"l⟦icr⟧*b⟦ecr⟧t)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., what you please.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A nice point; a subtilty; a debatable
point.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These are your <qex>quodlibets</qex>, but no learning.</q>
<rj><qau>P. Fletcher.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>A medley improvised by several
performers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quodlibetarian</ent>⟦br⟧
